calc_feature_desc

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
calc_feature_desc -  This function needs to be overridden to display the actual message to the feature.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
string calc_feature_desc(mapping direc,
int night,
int visibility)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^direc%^RESET%^ - the directions and distances
%^BOLD%^night%^RESET%^ - the night feature
.EI

.SH Returns
.SI 5
the feature descriptions
.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/std/room/inherit/terrain_map/feature_base.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This function needs to be overridden to display the actual
message to the feature.  The direc argument is a mapping of the
form, key = direction, value = distance.
.EP

